---

## ğŸ§© 3. Test Design Approach

| Technique | Description | Example |
|------------|--------------|----------|
| **Equivalence Partitioning (EP)** | Group valid/invalid inputs into partitions | Search field input validation |
| **Boundary Value Analysis (BVA)** | Check edges of input ranges | Price range filter limits |
| **Decision Table Testing** | Combine conditions and expected outputs | Checkout + payment flow |
| **State Transition Testing** | Validate state changes | Cart â†’ Checkout â†’ Order |
| **Error Guessing** | Identify likely user or system errors | Invalid payment input, broken image links |

---

