| TC_01 | Verify search by title | â€œAtomic Habitsâ€ | 1. Enter title in search box <br> 2. Click **Search** | Books titled *Atomic Habits* appear | EP |
| TC_02 | Filter by category | Category = â€œFictionâ€ | Select â€œFictionâ€ from filter | Only fiction books are displayed | EP |
| TC_03 | Sort by price ascending | Sort option = â€œLow to Highâ€ | Apply sort | Book list arranged ascendingly by price | Decision Table |
| TC_04 | Boundary test on price range | Min = 0, Max = 5000 | Apply filter | All books priced â‰¤ 5000 appear | BVA |
| TC_05 | Invalid filter input | Category = â€œ123$$$â€ | Type in invalid category | Validation error or empty results displayed | Error Guessing |

